<para id="fs-id1170572247756">In <link target-id="CNX_Calc_Figure_01_05_001"/>, we graph both <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mi>x</m:mi><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> and <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:msup><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:msup></m:mrow></m:math> to show how the graphs differ.</para>
